SIDDWM                                        siddwm is dumb dumb window manager
________________________________________________________________________________

SIDDWM is a fork of sowm
The XLib version has a few fixes and new features.
The Xcb version is still a work in progress.

*Checkout the pull requests for the different versions


COMMON FEATURE
________________________________________________________________________________

- Floating only.
- Fullscreen toggle.
- Window centering.
- Mix of mouse and keyboard workflow.
- Focus with cursor .
- Alt-Tab window focusing.
- All windows die on exit.
- No window borders.
- No ICCCM
- No EWMH.
- etc etc etc


